    <item>
      <title>Version 1.0.14</title>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Jun 2026 12:02:38 +0000</pubDate>
      <sparkle:version>12</sparkle:version>
      <sparkle:shortVersionString>1.0.14</sparkle:shortVersionString>
      <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>26.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
      <description><![CDATA[
        <b>Fixes.</b>
        <ul>
          <li>Groups and chats you've left no longer reappear in the reply queue.</li>
          <li>Deleted or edited messages no longer linger in search, and “Clear all local data” now fully wipes the on-device search index.</li>
          <li>Background indexing no longer gets stuck on link-only messages (fixes a CPU/battery drain).</li>
        </ul>
        <b>New.</b>
        <ul>
          <li>Reply drafts now adapt to your own writing style.</li>
          <li>Managed AI now runs on Gemini — faster and lower cost.</li>
        </ul>
      ]]></description>
      <enclosure url="https://github.com/0xpratzyy/pidgy-releases/releases/download/v1.0.14/Pidgy-922e6af.dmg"
