      <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>26.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
      <description><![CDATA[
        <b>Fixes.</b>
        <ul>
          <li>Log out works reliably now — it signs you out, clears local data, and returns to the login screen (it could previously hang or crash).</li>
